#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.airy.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.special.airy"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.airy.airy:1 of
msgid "Airy functions and their derivatives."
msgstr "Airy 函数及其导数。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.airy.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.airy.airy:3 of
msgid "Real or complex argument."
msgstr "实数或复数参数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.airy.airy:5 of
msgid "Optional output arrays for the function values"
msgstr "可选的函数值输出数组"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.airy.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.airy.airy:8 of
msgid ""
"**Ai, Aip, Bi, Bip** -- Airy functions Ai and Bi, and their derivatives "
"Aip and Bip."
msgstr "**Ai, Aip, Bi, Bip** -- Airy 函数 Ai 和 Bi，以及它们的导数 Aip 和 Bip。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.airy.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.airy.airy:13 of
msgid ":py:obj:`airye`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.airy.airy:14 of
msgid "exponentially scaled Airy functions."
msgstr "指数缩放的 Airy 函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.airy.airy:17 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.airy.airy:18 of
msgid "The Airy functions Ai and Bi are two independent solutions of"
msgstr "Airy 函数 Ai 和 Bi 是以下方程的两个独立解："

#: maxframe.tensor.special.airy.airy:20 of
msgid ""
"y''(x) = x y(x).\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.airy.airy:22 of
msgid ""
"For real `z` in [-10, 10], the computation is carried out by calling the "
"Cephes [1]_ `airy` routine, which uses power series summation for small "
"`z` and rational minimax approximations for large `z`."
msgstr ""
"对于区间 [-10, 10] 内的实数 `z`，通过调用 Cephes [1]_ 的 `airy` 程序进行"
"计算，该程序对小 `z` 使用幂级数求和，对大 `z` 使用有理极小极大逼近。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.airy.airy:26 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Outside this range, the AMOS [2]_ `zairy` and `zbiry` routines are "
"employed.  They are computed using power series for :math:`|z| < 1` and "
"the following relations to modified Bessel functions for larger `z` "
"(where :math:`t \\equiv 2 z^{3/2}/3`):"
msgstr ""
"在此区间之外，使用 AMOS [2]_ 的 `zairy` 和 `zbiry` 程序。对于 :math:`|z| "
"< 1` 使用幂级数计算，对于较大的 `z` 使用以下与修正贝塞尔函数的关系进行"
"计算（其中 :math:`t \\equiv 2 z^{3/2}/3`）："

#: maxframe.tensor.special.airy.airy:31 of
msgid ""
"Ai(z) = \\frac{1}{\\pi \\sqrt{3}} K_{1/3}(t)\n"
"\n"
"Ai'(z) = -\\frac{z}{\\pi \\sqrt{3}} K_{2/3}(t)\n"
"\n"
"Bi(z) = \\sqrt{\\frac{z}{3}} \\left(I_{-1/3}(t) + I_{1/3}(t) \\right)\n"
"\n"
"Bi'(z) = \\frac{z}{\\sqrt{3}} \\left(I_{-2/3}(t) + I_{2/3}(t)\\right)"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.airy.airy:42 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.airy.airy:43 of
msgid "Cephes Mathematical Functions Library, http://www.netlib.org/cephes/"
msgstr "Cephes 数学函数库，http://www.netlib.org/cephes/"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.airy.airy:45 of
msgid ""
"Donald E. Amos, \"AMOS, A Portable Package for Bessel Functions of a "
"Complex Argument and Nonnegative Order\", http://netlib.org/amos/"
msgstr ""
"Donald E. Amos, \"AMOS, 一个用于复数参数和非负阶贝塞尔函数的可移植程序包"
"\", http://netlib.org/amos/"

